name: Under 5 Buds
blurb: Introducing football skills through fun training activities.

name: Under 6 Youth
blurb: Continuing to build on football skills leading to understanding of the 5-a-side game. game play will develop through training and later tournament participation and friendly 5-a-side games.

name: Under 7 Youth
blurb: Developing game play through training and Saturday morning league matches. This is the youngest age group in the Invicta Primary League at 5-a-side. League football will also be supplemented by competition games and tournaments as appropriate.

name: Under 7 Blues
blurb: Developing game play through training and Saturday morning league matches. This is the youngest age group in the Invicta Primary League at 5-a-side. League football will also be supplemented by competition games and tournaments as appropriate

name: Under 7 Colts
blurb: For those not yet ready to play regularly in the Invicta Primary League our U7 Colts enables development of football skills and confidence.
